WEBVTT

00:02.213 --> 00:03.254
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...
 Man: WE'VE GOT A BODY OVER HERE!

00:03.254 --> 00:04.465
THE CORONER CHECKED
HER DENTAL RECORDS.

00:04.465 --> 00:05.836
IT'S DEFINITELY
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

00:05.836 --> 00:07.128
Victoria's voice:
MY DEAREST MARGAUX,

00:07.128 --> 00:09.050
I'VE DECIDED TO END MY LIFE.

00:09.050 --> 00:12.933
YOU HAVE TWO DAYS TO CLEAR
MY NAME. YOUR MOVE, AMANDA.

00:12.933 --> 00:14.515
SOMEONE BROKE IN HERE
AND ATTACKED VICTORIA.

00:14.515 --> 00:17.348
THIS WASN'T A SUICIDE AT ALL.
THIS WAS MURDER.

00:17.348 --> 00:20.141
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?
 I WAS CALLED BACK
FOR QUESTIONING.

00:20.141 --> 00:21.772
ISN'T THIS A CONFLICT
OF INTEREST,

00:21.772 --> 00:22.983
WORKING ON A CASE
THAT INVOLVES YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

00:22.983 --> 00:24.024
WE BROKE UP THE NIGHT
YOU LEFT.

00:24.024 --> 00:26.407
SHE RAN TO THE AIRPORT
TO STOP YOU. SHE CHOSE YOU.

00:26.407 --> 00:27.988
IT'S A FORM OF LYMPHOMA.

00:27.988 --> 00:31.112
THEY GOT IT EARLY, AND I'M
GETTING CUTTING-EDGE TREATMENT.

00:31.112 --> 00:33.033
VICTORIA ASKED ME TO PASS ALONG
A MESSAGE.

00:33.033 --> 00:34.455
I'M GOING TO MAKE IT APPEAR

00:34.455 --> 00:36.617
AS IF YOU MURDERED ME
IN YOUR OWN HOME.

00:36.617 --> 00:37.748
AMANDA CLARKE,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

00:37.748 --> 00:38.869
FOR THE MURDER
OF VICTORIA GRAYSON.

00:38.869 --> 00:40.121
VICTORIA SET ME UP.
 CUFF HER.

00:40.121 --> 00:42.253
JACK, I DIDN'T DO IT.
SHE PLANNED THIS!

00:42.253 --> 00:43.964
I'M INNOCENT!

00:46.006 --> 00:48.929
Man: THEY'RE GOING FOR
THE BRASS RING --

00:48.929 --> 00:50.631
MURDER ONE,
SPECIAL CIRCUMSTANCES,

00:50.631 --> 00:52.553
AND THEY LIKE THEIR ODDS.

00:52.553 --> 00:54.595
THE STATE'S GOING TO ARGUE THAT
A WEEK AFTER YOU WENT ON TV

00:54.595 --> 00:58.179
AND TOLD THE WORLD HOW MUCH
YOU HATE VICTORIA GRAYSON,

00:58.179 --> 01:00.271
YOU TERRORIZED HER
IN A PARKING GARAGE,

01:00.271 --> 01:02.853
BROKE INTO HER PENTHOUSE,
ATTACKED HER,

01:02.853 --> 01:04.144
THEN YOU LOCKED HER
IN YOUR OWN HOME,

01:04.144 --> 01:05.816
WHICH YOU BURNED TO THE GROUND

01:05.816 --> 01:09.029
IN AN ATTEMPT TO MAKE IT LOOK
LIKE SHE KILLED HERSELF.

01:09.029 --> 01:12.153
AND THIS IS HER SUICIDE NOTE
THAT I ALLEGEDLY FORGED.

01:12.153 --> 01:14.285
WHICH THEY'LL HAVE YOU READ
ALOUD AT TRIAL.

01:14.285 --> 01:16.197
BUT THIS IS
 VICTORIA'S HANDWRITING.

01:16.197 --> 01:19.039
D.A.'s EXPERTS FOUND
SMALL DISCREPANCIES

01:19.039 --> 01:21.041
WHICH WILL PROVE IT'S A FAKE,

01:21.041 --> 01:22.082
AND THEIR ARGUMENT WILL BE THAT

01:22.082 --> 01:23.544
YOU COULDN'T HAVE ACCOMPLISHED
HALF OF WHAT YOU DID

01:23.544 --> 01:27.007
AS "EMILY THORNE"
WITHOUT DOING PLENTY OF FORGING.

01:27.007 --> 01:28.419
WHICH IS WHY
I SAY IT AGAIN --

01:28.419 --> 01:32.012
AT LEAST LET ME TRY TO NEGOTIATE
A PLEA TO LESSER CHARGES.

01:32.012 --> 01:33.304
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

01:34.675 --> 01:38.219
IF YOU'RE FOUND GUILTY OF
MURDER ONE, IT'S LIFE IN PRISON.

01:38.219 --> 01:40.221
SECOND DEGREE MIGHT
HAVE YOU OUT IN --

01:40.221 --> 01:42.102
I'M NOT PLEADING GUILTY
TO ANYTHING.

01:42.102 --> 01:46.567
THERE'S NOTHING TO NEGOTIATE.
JUST GET ME BAILED OUT.

01:46.567 --> 01:49.400
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]
 Man: OVER HERE, GUYS! OVER HERE!
WHAT ARE WE GONNA SAY TODAY?

01:49.400 --> 01:50.941
Woman: ONE PICTURE!
 Man: WHAT'S GOING ON?

01:50.941 --> 01:52.493
Woman: RIGHT HERE! RIGHT HERE!

01:52.493 --> 01:53.904
DAVID.
 HEY.

01:53.904 --> 01:55.115
HOW'D IT GO?

01:55.115 --> 01:57.498
THE CHEMO? OH, DAY AT THE SPA.

01:57.498 --> 01:58.949
HE'S A TROOPER.

01:58.949 --> 02:00.201
HAVE YOU SEEN AMANDA YET?

02:00.201 --> 02:02.203
NO, THEY HAVEN'T
BROUGHT HER OUT.

02:02.203 --> 02:05.296
BUT I MAY HAVE JUST TRACKED DOWN
OUR MISSING FRIEND --

02:05.296 --> 02:07.007
VICTORIA'S PARTNER IN CRIME.

02:07.007 --> 02:08.799
TREADWELL?
 MM-HMM.

02:08.799 --> 02:10.711
I'VE BEEN HIJACKING FEEDS
FROM ALL OVER THE WEB,

02:10.711 --> 02:12.012
MOSTLY SECURITY CAM FOOTAGE,

02:12.012 --> 02:14.175
RUNNING IT THROUGH
FACIAL RECOGNITION SOFTWARE.

02:14.175 --> 02:16.387
WHEN I NARROWED IT DOWN
TO SMUG AND TRAITOROUS,

02:16.387 --> 02:17.928
THAT'S WHAT CAME UP.

02:17.928 --> 02:20.471
THAT'S MASON. WHERE IS THAT?
IS THAT A TRAILER PARK?

02:20.471 --> 02:21.722
HMM, THAT'S A GOOD EYE.

02:21.722 --> 02:23.474
ABOUT 11 OF THEM
IN A 100-MILE RADIUS.

02:23.474 --> 02:25.025
I'M TRYING TO NARROW IT DOWN.

02:25.025 --> 02:28.439
LEAVE IT TO MASON TREADWELL TO
TAKE A LIMO TO A TRAILER PARK.

02:28.439 --> 02:30.191
[ CHUCKLES ]
 Man: ALL RISE.

02:30.191 --> 02:32.693
THE HONORABLE JUDGE MOSS
PRESIDING.

02:38.199 --> 02:40.991
MS. CLARKE,
WE'RE READY FOR YOU NOW.

02:54.134 --> 02:56.557
[ CHAIR WHEELS ROLL ]

02:56.557 --> 02:59.760
Man: COURT IS NOW IN SESSION.
YOU MAY BE SEATED.

03:07.728 --> 03:10.231
Margaux: SO YOU DON'T SEE
THE PROBLEM? READ IT.

03:10.231 --> 03:11.652
"AMANDA CLARKE
TO BE ARRAIGNED."

03:11.652 --> 03:14.655
NO, ALLEGED KILLER
 AMANDA CLARKE TO BE ARRAIGNED.

03:14.655 --> 03:16.076
PUT IT IN THE STYLE SHEET.

03:16.076 --> 03:18.078
FROM HERE ON,
EVERY TIME WE USE HER NAME,

03:18.078 --> 03:20.581
IT'S "ALLEGED KILLER
AMANDA CLARKE."

03:20.581 --> 03:21.992
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS,
DOOR OPENS ]

03:23.584 --> 03:26.247
GIVE ME FIVE MINUTES.

03:26.247 --> 03:29.540
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

03:29.540 --> 03:32.543
LOUISE.
BETWEEN MURDER TRIAL COVERAGE

03:32.543 --> 03:34.925
AND DESIGNING
NEW CORPORATE HEADQUARTERS,

03:34.925 --> 03:37.758
I'M SORRY, I COMPLETELY FORGOT
TO CALL YOU BACK.

03:37.758 --> 03:39.009
WHEN DO YOU SLEEP?

03:39.009 --> 03:41.512
WELL, RIGHT NOW,
IT'S BETTER THAN I DON'T.

03:41.512 --> 03:43.223
WHAT DID YOU NEED?

03:43.223 --> 03:45.436
WELL, IT'S REGARDING
THE FUNERAL.

03:45.436 --> 03:46.767
UM, THE CHURCH IS SET...
 MM-HMM.

03:46.767 --> 03:48.609
AND I PUT OUT THE RELEASE.

03:48.609 --> 03:49.810
BUT WHEN I WENT
TO THE PENTHOUSE

03:49.810 --> 03:51.692
TO GET SOME PHOTOGRAPHS
FOR THE PROGRAM,

03:51.692 --> 03:52.983
I-I COULDN'T GET IN.

03:52.983 --> 03:54.154
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

03:54.154 --> 03:57.658
WELL, THE CONCIERGE SAID THAT
ONCE THE POLICE WERE THROUGH,

03:57.658 --> 04:01.622
THE PENTHOUSE WAS ORDERED SEALED
BY THE EXECUTOR OF HER ESTATE?

04:01.622 --> 04:02.783
MM.
 I TRIED TO EXPLAIN TO THEM

04:02.783 --> 04:04.955
THAT I WAS LIKE A DAUGHTER
TO VICTORIA, BUT --

04:04.955 --> 04:08.869
BUT THE EXECUTOR IS
HER REAL DAUGHTER -- CHARLOTTE.

04:10.961 --> 04:12.042
[ Whispers ] YEAH.

04:12.042 --> 04:15.175
WELL, UM...IT'S LOCKED UP
UNTIL PROBATE,

04:15.175 --> 04:16.587
AND...
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

04:16.587 --> 04:19.470
IT'S THE ONLY PLACE
WHERE I CAN STILL FEEL HER.

04:19.470 --> 04:23.183
YOU KNOW, WITH ALL HER THINGS
AND PICTURES AND...

04:23.183 --> 04:26.347
I'D REALLY LIKE TO BE THERE
ONE MORE TIME TO SAY GOOD-BYE.

04:26.347 --> 04:27.768
I'D BREAK IN IF I COULD.

04:27.768 --> 04:30.601
OH, SWEETHEART.
NO, PLEASE DON'T.

04:30.601 --> 04:32.983
NO, I'LL TRY TO GET YOU
A PHONE NUMBER.

04:32.983 --> 04:34.024
THANK YOU.

04:34.024 --> 04:36.857
[ Whispers ] OKAY.

04:36.857 --> 04:39.990
I ALSO HAVE YOU DOING A READING
AFTER THE MINISTER.

04:39.990 --> 04:41.572
IT'S A BEAUTIFUL
ROBERT FROST POEM.

04:41.572 --> 04:44.114
NO. NO, I DON'T WANT
TO SPEAK.

04:44.114 --> 04:47.167
NO, IT'S TOO PUBLIC,
TOO PERSONAL.

04:47.167 --> 04:48.329
AFTER WHAT WE'VE BEEN THROUGH,

04:48.329 --> 04:50.541
I'D BE AFRAID I WOULD NEVER
STOP CRYING.

04:50.541 --> 04:53.083
WE ALL NEED TO GRIEVE, MARGAUX.

04:54.505 --> 04:57.217
THIS IS HOW I GRIEVE.

04:59.049 --> 05:00.551
I CAN'T URGE STRONGLY ENOUGH

05:00.551 --> 05:02.553
THE DEFENDANT BE HELD
 WITHOUT BAIL.

05:02.553 --> 05:03.844
YOUR HONOR,
THIS IS AN ARRAIGNMENT,

05:03.844 --> 05:05.516
NOT THE A.D.A.'s
PRESS CONFERENCE.
 ON LIVE TV,

05:05.516 --> 05:07.348
MS. CLARKE HERSELF TOLD US
SHE'S A FLIGHT RISK...

05:07.348 --> 05:09.189
MY CLIENT ABSOLUTELY SHOULD
BE ALLOWED TO BOND OUT.

05:09.189 --> 05:11.932
DETAILING HER VAST SKILLS
IN HIDING

05:11.932 --> 05:14.895
HER IDENTITY AND METING OUT...
 SHE HAS A SPOTLESS RECORD...

05:14.895 --> 05:16.857
VIGILANTE JUSTICE.
 STRONG TIES TO COMMUNITY
AND FAMILY.

05:16.857 --> 05:18.148
STRONG TIES?

05:18.148 --> 05:20.200
SHE SPENT FOUR YEARS TERRORIZING
THIS COMMUNITY.

05:20.200 --> 05:21.742
TO REDEEM A FATHER
WHO IS STILL RECOVERING

05:21.742 --> 05:24.204
FROM THE EFFECTS OF BEING
WRONGLY CONVICTED.
 THAT DOES --

05:24.204 --> 05:27.538
ENOUGH! NOBODY HERE IS BEING
PAID BY THE WORD.

05:27.538 --> 05:30.210
MS. CLARKE, MY THOUGHTS.

05:30.210 --> 05:33.754
I WILL GRANT BAIL, BUT I DO SO
WITH GREAT CONCERN

05:33.754 --> 05:36.417
AND UNDER THE STRICTEST
OF CONDITIONS.

05:36.417 --> 05:40.220
IF I HEAR EVEN A RUMOR
THAT MY CONDITIONS FOR RELEASE

05:40.220 --> 05:43.093
HAVE BEEN VIOLATED, I WILL
HAVE YOU LOCKED UP SO FAST

05:43.093 --> 05:46.677
YOUR INSCRUTABLE LITTLE HEAD
WILL SPIN.

05:46.677 --> 05:48.348
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

05:48.348 --> 05:50.731
YES, I DO, YOUR HONOR.

05:50.731 --> 05:53.684
BAIL IS SET AT $2 MILLION.

05:53.684 --> 05:56.527
NOW, AS FOR MY CONDITIONS...

05:56.527 --> 05:59.069
[ BEEPS ]
 IF YOU TAKE A STEP
OFF THE PROPERTY,

05:59.069 --> 06:02.863
IF THE MONITOR IS REMOVED,
DISABLED, OR TAMPERED WITH,

06:02.863 --> 06:04.575
SUFFOLK COUNTY P.D.,
STATE POLICE,

06:04.575 --> 06:06.987
AND THE U.S. MARSHAL'S OFFICE
WILL BE IMMEDIATELY NOTIFIED,

06:06.987 --> 06:08.749
PER ORDER OF THE COURT.

06:08.749 --> 06:11.702
IS THAT CLEAR?

06:11.702 --> 06:13.163
EMILY?

06:13.163 --> 06:14.415
IT'S CLEAR. TELL HIM.

06:14.415 --> 06:17.087
YES. YES, IT'S CLEAR.

06:17.087 --> 06:18.208
OKAY.

06:18.208 --> 06:20.841
THEN WE'LL LEAVE YOU TO IT.

06:23.263 --> 06:25.175
LOOK, BEN...

06:25.175 --> 06:27.217
I'M SORRY YOU GOT STUCK
WITH THIS GIG.

06:27.217 --> 06:28.509
I DIDN'T GET STUCK WITH IT.

06:28.509 --> 06:30.140
I TOLD DETECTIVE YAMADA
THAT I'M FAMILIAR

06:30.140 --> 06:31.432
WITH THE HOUSE
AND THE PROPERTY.

06:31.432 --> 06:35.606
SO YOU VOLUNTEERED TO BE
THE PERSON TO KEEP ME LOCKED UP.

06:35.606 --> 06:37.568
WOW. [ CHUCKLES ]

06:37.568 --> 06:39.480
WE'VE REALLY COME A LONG WAY
IN THE PAST FEW WEEKS.

06:39.480 --> 06:40.981
IT'S NOTHING PERSONAL, EMILY.

06:40.981 --> 06:43.193
I KNOW YOU BETTER
THAN ANYONE ON THE FORCE,

06:43.193 --> 06:44.985
AND SO I KNOW THAT RIGHT NOW,

06:44.985 --> 06:47.197
YOU ARE ALREADY PONDERING A WAY
TO GET OUT OF THAT THING.

06:47.197 --> 06:51.371
I VOLUNTEERED SO THAT I COULD BE
THE ONE TO TELL YOU DON'T DO IT,

06:51.371 --> 06:54.124
THAT YOU WILL GET CAUGHT.

07:15.105 --> 07:16.817
AFTER WE CATCH HIM,
THE PLAN IS WHAT?

07:16.817 --> 07:18.108
LOOK, MASON HAS TO HAVE
THE FOOTAGE

07:18.108 --> 07:20.060
OF VICTORIA ADMITTING
THAT SHE FRAMED ME.

07:20.060 --> 07:22.483
AND IF HE DOESN'T, I DRAG HIM
TO COURT BY HIS FEET.

07:22.483 --> 07:24.024
YOUR DAD'S OUT COLD.

07:24.024 --> 07:26.066
THAT REGIMEN'S
DOING A NUMBER ON HIM.

07:26.066 --> 07:28.068
I KNOW.

07:28.068 --> 07:29.870
BUT HE SAYS...
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

07:29.870 --> 07:33.453
THAT'S HOW HE KNOWS
IT'S WORKING. SO...

07:33.453 --> 07:34.875
THANK YOU FOR TAKING HIM.

07:34.875 --> 07:37.998
OF COURSE. IT'S WHY I STAYED.

07:37.998 --> 07:39.339
WHERE ARE WE?

07:39.339 --> 07:42.172
WE REJECTED MY OFFER
TO GO AFTER MASON TREADWELL,

07:42.172 --> 07:43.463
OR TO SEND YOU.

07:43.463 --> 07:45.506
I AM NOT PUTTING ANYONE ELSE
ON HIS RADAR.

07:45.506 --> 07:46.587
BUT YOU FOUND THE TRAILER PARK?

07:46.587 --> 07:49.179
YEAH, IT'S IN STONY BROOK.
IT'S AN HOUR AWAY.

07:49.179 --> 07:50.971
AND YOU THINK YOU'RE GONNA
GET OUT OF HERE

07:50.971 --> 07:53.013
WITHOUT TRIGGERING ANY ALARMS?
 WE'RE WORKING ON IT.

07:53.013 --> 07:55.686
[ SIGHS ] I GOT
THIS ANKLE MONITOR VERY USED

07:55.686 --> 07:57.097
FROM AN ARMY NAVY STORE.

07:57.097 --> 08:00.901
AND AFTER A FEW HIGH-TECH,
HIGHLY COMPLICATED SWITCHEROOS,

08:00.901 --> 08:02.192
BOOM --

08:02.192 --> 08:03.363
THE ONE ON YOUR LEG
SHOULD GO OFF-LINE,

08:03.363 --> 08:06.527
AND THIS WILL BECOME
THE LIVE MONITOR AND STAY HERE.

08:06.527 --> 08:08.659
AND I JUST WALK OUT THE DOOR?

08:08.659 --> 08:10.200
THEORETICALLY.

08:11.872 --> 08:14.665
OKAY, LOOK, I KNOW THAT WORD
DOESN'T RADIATE CONFIDENCE.

08:14.665 --> 08:17.918
GUYS, I GOTTA FOCUS HERE.

08:19.750 --> 08:22.122
CAN I TALK TO YOU OUTSIDE?

08:22.122 --> 08:26.336
SURE. YEAH. ANYWHERE THAT'S
LESS THAN 6 FEET FROM THE DOOR.

08:32.222 --> 08:34.224
WHO KNEW VICTORIA HAD IT
IN HER?

08:34.224 --> 08:37.727
WELL, I DID. BUT THERE'S NO WAY
SHE PULLED IT OFF ALONE.

08:37.727 --> 08:40.640
THIS PLAN HAD A LOT
OF MOVING PARTS.

08:40.640 --> 08:42.693
I THINK MASON WAS
JUST ONE OF THEM.

08:42.693 --> 08:44.063
I COULD SEE
IF MARGAUX KNOWS ANYTHING.

08:44.063 --> 08:47.447
NO. NO, I DON'T WANNA PULL YOU
INTO THIS ANY FURTHER.

08:47.447 --> 08:50.070
I'M HERE BY CHOICE.

08:53.073 --> 08:55.245
BUT I'D LOVE TO ASK YOU
SOMETHING.

09:00.460 --> 09:02.212
LOOK,
I KNOW THAT EVERYTHING

09:02.212 --> 09:04.044
IS SPINNING OUT OF CONTROL --
THE ARREST,

09:04.044 --> 09:06.166
YOUR...
[ INHALES DEEPLY ] DAD,

09:06.166 --> 09:07.427
AND YOU'RE JUST TRYING TO
KEEP YOUR HEAD ABOVE WATER,

09:07.427 --> 09:10.380
SO IT'S NOT THE BEST TIME
FOR THIS CONVERSATION, BUT...

09:13.133 --> 09:14.595
THE OTHER NIGHT, BEFORE YOU GOT
ARRESTED, I HEARD THAT

09:14.595 --> 09:16.346
YOU CAME TO THE AIRPORT
TO TELL ME NOT TO LEAVE.

09:16.346 --> 09:19.059
AND I JUST....

09:19.059 --> 09:23.984
I JUST HAVE TO KNOW...

09:23.984 --> 09:25.896
IS THAT TRUE?

09:29.990 --> 09:31.031
YES.

09:33.193 --> 09:34.995
I WANTED YOU TO STAY.

09:34.995 --> 09:37.577
I...

09:37.577 --> 09:39.369
I WANT YOU TO STAY.

09:39.369 --> 09:42.002
WHEN NOLAN TOLD ME
THAT YOU WERE LEAVING,

09:42.002 --> 09:44.124
I... [ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

09:45.255 --> 09:48.258
I REALIZED HOW BADLY
I HAD MESSED ALL THIS UP.

09:48.258 --> 09:51.171
SO I WENT AFTER YOU.

09:51.171 --> 09:53.593
I WAS FIVE MINUTES TOO LATE.

09:53.593 --> 09:56.266
OR MAYBE...
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

09:56.266 --> 09:58.178
FOUR YEARS TOO LATE.

09:58.178 --> 10:00.891
BUT...

10:00.891 --> 10:03.483
I WANNA BE WITH YOU.

10:03.483 --> 10:07.107
THAT'S WHY I NEED
ALL OF THIS TO WORK,

10:07.107 --> 10:08.488
WHY I'M GOING AFTER MASON,

10:08.488 --> 10:11.281
IF I HAVE TO CUT
MY DAMN FOOT OFF.

10:14.284 --> 10:17.948
I WANT US
TO HAVE THAT CHANCE.

10:22.372 --> 10:23.954
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

10:23.954 --> 10:26.126
HEY.

10:26.126 --> 10:28.128
UM... [CLEARS THROAT ]
SO SORRY TO INTERRUPT.

10:28.128 --> 10:30.550
I NEED YOUR ANKLE INSIDE
RIGHT NOW, EMS.

10:30.550 --> 10:33.804
WE'VE GOT A REALLY SMALL WINDOW
OF TIME TO SWAP FREQUENCIES

10:33.804 --> 10:35.215
AND PULL THIS OFF.

10:41.141 --> 10:42.392
EMS.

10:50.691 --> 10:52.442
[ Whispers ] LET'S DO THIS.

10:53.984 --> 10:58.038
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:58.038 --> 10:59.079
[ MAN SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

10:59.079 --> 11:01.201
REHAB IS LIKE DIETING.

11:01.201 --> 11:03.243
WEEK ONE IS THE WORST.

11:03.243 --> 11:04.995
YOU'RE DOING GREAT.

11:04.995 --> 11:06.416
THANK YOU.

11:06.416 --> 11:07.627
OKAY.

11:07.627 --> 11:08.999
THANKS.

11:10.210 --> 11:12.052
CHARLOTTE GRAYSON?

11:12.052 --> 11:14.094
IT'S CLARKE. DO I KNOW YOU?

11:14.094 --> 11:17.928
[ Voice breaks ]
I'M SO SORRY FOR YOUR LOSS.

11:17.928 --> 11:19.179
UH...

11:19.179 --> 11:21.011
YOU LOOK JUST LIKE
YOUR DEAR MOTHER.

11:21.011 --> 11:23.183
[ SNIFFLES ]
 HAVE WE MET?

11:23.183 --> 11:26.937
NO. I'M SORRY. NOT OFFICIALLY.
I'M LOUISE. LOUISE ELLIS?

11:26.937 --> 11:30.520
OH. YOU'VE BEEN LEAVING ME
MESSAGES ABOUT THE FUNERAL.

11:30.520 --> 11:32.863
YES. IT WAS PRESSING
THAT I TALK TO YOU

11:32.863 --> 11:35.235
BECAUSE, AS I MAY HAVE
MENTIONED,

11:35.235 --> 11:38.989
I WOULD LIKE TO INCLUDE
SOME PHOTOGRAPHS AND MEMENTOS

11:38.989 --> 11:40.490
OF YOUR MOTHER'S AMAZING LIFE

11:40.490 --> 11:44.164
TO BRING SOLACE
TO THOSE SHE LEFT BEHIND.

11:44.164 --> 11:46.747
I-I DO, HOWEVER,
NEED YOUR PERMISSION

11:46.747 --> 11:48.208
TO ACCESS HER PENTHOUSE.

11:48.208 --> 11:50.380
YEAH, THE THING ABOUT
THE FUNERAL --

11:50.380 --> 11:53.043
OH, I'M SO SORRY. I OVERSTEPPED.

11:53.043 --> 11:55.175
YOU WOULD LIKE TO PLAN IT.

11:55.175 --> 11:57.597
NO.

11:57.597 --> 12:01.221
IT'S THAT I'M NOT GOING,
LET ALONE PLANNING ONE.

12:01.221 --> 12:04.104
I DON'T KNOW WHICH
VICTORIA GRAYSON YOU MET,

12:04.104 --> 12:06.726
BUT MY MINE WAS
THE MOST MANIPULATIVE HUMAN

12:06.726 --> 12:08.148
I'VE EVER KNOWN.

12:08.148 --> 12:10.190
[ Whispers ]
YOU DON'T MEAN THAT.

12:10.190 --> 12:12.112
YOU'RE CLEARLY IN SHOCK

12:12.112 --> 12:13.523
OR -- OR DENIAL.

12:13.523 --> 12:16.356
[ SCOFFS ] THE ONLY
AMAZING THING ABOUT VICTORIA

12:16.356 --> 12:19.159
WAS HER ABILITY TO GET WHAT
SHE WANTED, NO MATTER THE COST.

12:19.159 --> 12:21.201
CHARLOTTE, SHE LIVED
FOR HER CHILDREN.

12:21.201 --> 12:23.123
AND IT'S IMPORTANT TO GRIEVE,

12:23.123 --> 12:25.325
AND I THINK THIS
MEMORIAL SERVICE WOULD REALLY --

12:25.325 --> 12:28.078
I'M ACTUALLY HEALTHIER
THAN I'VE EVER BEEN.

12:28.078 --> 12:31.081
AND AS FOR GRIEVING,
I'VE DONE MY SHARE YEARS AGO,

12:31.081 --> 12:34.835
THE FIRST TIME MY MOTHER "DIED"
AND THEN DISAPPEARED.

12:36.006 --> 12:38.008
I'M...SORRY.
SHE DID WHAT NOW?

12:38.008 --> 12:40.510
I HAVE TO GET TO THE STABLES.
EQUINE THERAPY.

12:40.510 --> 12:42.432
IT WAS NICE MEETING YOU.

12:42.432 --> 12:44.344
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT. UM...

12:44.344 --> 12:46.596
WHAT ABOUT HER BELONGINGS?

12:46.596 --> 12:48.979
I'M HAVING THEM BOXED UP
AND SHIPPED TO CHARITY.

12:50.690 --> 12:53.273
BUT DON'T YOU WANT SOMETHING
TO REMEMBER HER BY?

12:54.815 --> 12:56.156
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

12:56.156 --> 12:57.988
YOU STOP CALLING ME,
AND I'LL TELL THE HOTEL

12:57.988 --> 13:00.200
YOU HAVE MY PERMISSION
TO ENTER HER PENTHOUSE.

13:00.200 --> 13:02.362
YOU TAKE WHATEVER'S GONNA
BRING YOU SOLACE.

13:11.751 --> 13:13.083
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

13:13.083 --> 13:15.005
DAD.

13:15.005 --> 13:16.086
ARE YOU OKAY? DID I WAKE YOU?

13:16.086 --> 13:18.378
I'M FINE.
ANSWER THE QUESTION.

13:18.378 --> 13:20.380
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

13:20.380 --> 13:23.183
IF SOMETHING GOES WRONG, I DON'T
WANT YOU TO BE COMPLICIT.

13:23.183 --> 13:24.474
"IF SOMETHING GOES WRONG"?

13:24.474 --> 13:26.226
LOOK AROUND YOU.
EVERYTHING'S GONE WRONG.

13:26.226 --> 13:28.768
TELL ME THAT YOU'RE NOT
GOING AFTER MASON.

13:31.191 --> 13:32.933
I HAVE TO.
I DON'T HAVE A CHOICE.

13:32.933 --> 13:33.984
IT'S CALLED HOUSE ARREST.

13:33.984 --> 13:36.066
YOU REALLY THINK
THAT YOU WON'T GET CAUGHT?

13:36.066 --> 13:38.698
YOUR FRIEND THE DETECTIVE
IS WAITING FOR YOU TO MESS UP.

13:38.698 --> 13:40.861
NOLAN IS ABOUT TO SET OFF ALARMS
AND SHORT OUT THE POWER GRID.

13:40.861 --> 13:42.652
HE BUILT A SECOND MONITOR,
AND HE'LL USE THE DIVERSION --

13:42.652 --> 13:44.704
I DON'T CARE IF HE BUILDS
A DAMN LASER BEAM

13:44.704 --> 13:46.156
THAT TURNS YOU INVISIBLE.

13:46.156 --> 13:47.327
IF THEY THROW ENOUGH COPS,
TROOPERS, AND MARSHALS AT YOU --

13:47.327 --> 13:48.828
AND THEY WILL --

13:48.828 --> 13:50.040
YOU WILL BE CAUGHT
AND PUT IN JAIL

13:50.040 --> 13:52.002
AND THEY WILL THROW AWAY
THE KEY UNTIL TRIAL.

13:52.002 --> 13:55.005
A TRIAL WHERE THEY WILL BURY ME
UNLESS I FIND MASON.

13:55.005 --> 13:58.008
AND I'M NOT GONNA SPEND THE REST
OF MY LIFE OR YOURS IN PRISON.

13:58.008 --> 13:59.920
[ EXHALES ]

13:59.920 --> 14:01.551
THEN I'LL GO.
 WHAT? NO.

14:01.551 --> 14:03.723
TELL ME WHERE HE IS. YOU STAY
HERE. I WILL FIND MASON.

14:03.723 --> 14:06.136
THAT'S A NICE OFFER, DAD.
 IT'S NOT AN OFFER.
TELL ME WHERE HE IS.

14:06.136 --> 14:09.139
STOP IT. YOU'RE NOT GOING.
YOU NEED TO GET YOUR REST.

14:09.139 --> 14:10.560
I AM YOUR FATHER,

14:10.560 --> 14:14.024
AND I AM TELLING YOU THAT
YOU'RE NOT LEAVING THIS HOUSE.

14:14.024 --> 14:15.065
[ ALARM BEEPING ]

14:15.065 --> 14:16.106
[ CLICK ]

14:17.477 --> 14:18.858
I'M SORRY, DAD.

14:30.370 --> 14:33.373
[ HORNS HONKING ]

14:36.456 --> 14:38.418
JACK.

14:38.418 --> 14:40.130
THIS CANNOT BE A COINCIDENCE.

14:40.130 --> 14:42.132
I REMEMBER YOU SAYING THIS IS
YOUR FAVORITE LUNCH SPOT,

14:42.132 --> 14:44.174
SO I TOOK A SHOT.

14:44.174 --> 14:46.766
I WANTED TO OFFER CONDOLENCES.

14:46.766 --> 14:48.268
I KNOW YOU AND VICTORIA
WERE CLOSE.

14:48.268 --> 14:50.140
YES.

14:50.140 --> 14:52.012
AND THERE'S...

14:52.012 --> 14:54.014
THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE.

14:54.014 --> 14:56.146
UH, JACK, I'M IN THE MIDDLE
OF A WORKING LUNCH.

14:56.146 --> 15:00.570
I-I WON'T TAKE LONG.
I JUST... [ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

15:00.570 --> 15:02.862
I WANTED TO KNOW IF YOU NOTICED
THE SAME THING THAT I DID.

15:02.862 --> 15:07.487
THE CIRCUMSTANCES AROUND
VICTORIA'S DEATH, THEY'RE...

15:07.487 --> 15:08.828
THEY'RE STRANGE.

15:08.828 --> 15:11.871
GO ASK THE PERSON WHO KILLED HER
TO EXPLAIN HERSELF.

15:11.871 --> 15:15.085
I'M NOT REALLY --
 BRAZEN VIOLENCE?
A TRAIL OF CLUES?

15:15.085 --> 15:17.167
IT'S SLOPPY.
IT'S NOT EMILY'S STYLE.

15:17.167 --> 15:19.799
AND WE BOTH KNOW SHE WOULD
NEVER TAKE SOMEONE'S LIFE.

15:19.799 --> 15:22.462
SO WHAT ARE YOU INSINUATING,
JACK?
 I'M NOT INSINUATING.

15:22.462 --> 15:24.344
I'M SAYING THAT IT LOOKS LIKE
SHE WAS SET UP.

15:25.885 --> 15:28.098
MARGAUX...

15:28.098 --> 15:30.220
IF YOU HAPPEN TO KNOW SOMETHING
ABOUT VICTORIA'S DEATH,

15:30.220 --> 15:31.811
NOW IS THE TIME TO SPEAK UP.

15:31.811 --> 15:33.603
THIS IS A KNEE-JERK REACTION
WITH YOU

15:33.603 --> 15:37.397
TO DEFEND EMILY NO MATTER WHAT,
EVEN WHEN SHE KILLS.

15:37.397 --> 15:39.980
VICTORIA SET HER UP.
SHE DIDN'T DO IT ALONE.

15:39.980 --> 15:42.402
AND WHAT DO YOU THINK HAPPENS
TO THE PARTNER SHE LEFT BEHIND

15:42.402 --> 15:45.155
WHEN IT ALL GETS EXPOSED?

15:45.155 --> 15:49.409
I HAD SUCH HOPE FOR YOU WHEN
I HEARD YOU LEFT FOR CALIFORNIA.

15:49.409 --> 15:52.452
YOU PULLED YOURSELF OUT
OF THE QUICKSAND AND ESCAPED.

15:52.452 --> 15:54.995
BUT YOU COULDN'T STAY AWAY.

15:54.995 --> 15:56.916
POOR JACK.

15:56.916 --> 15:58.578
WORRY ABOUT YOURSELF.
I'LL BE OKAY.

15:58.578 --> 16:00.000
NO, YOU WON'T.

16:00.000 --> 16:03.083
YOU HITCHED YOUR WAGON
TO A DAMAGED PSYCHOTIC HORSE,

16:03.083 --> 16:06.006
AND SHE'S PULLING YOU
RIGHT OFF A CLIFF.

16:06.006 --> 16:07.387
WHAT'S MY AFTERNOON LIKE?

16:07.387 --> 16:09.139
EDITORIAL PRE-CALL,
BUDGET MEETING,

16:09.139 --> 16:11.431
AND YOUR JEWELER SAID HE CAN
GET YOU IN TOMORROW.

16:13.143 --> 16:14.764
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

16:14.764 --> 16:16.556
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

16:21.101 --> 16:23.403
NOLAN, IT'S DAVID.

16:23.403 --> 16:25.025
I'M STILL...

16:25.025 --> 16:27.027
WELL, OBVIOUSLY, I'M...

16:27.027 --> 16:28.028
JUST CALL ME.

16:30.780 --> 16:33.033
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

16:43.833 --> 16:45.505
AH! DETECTIVE HUNTER.

16:45.505 --> 16:47.677
MR. CLARKE. HOW YOU FEELING?

16:47.677 --> 16:48.928
I WAS SO SORRY TO HEAR....

16:48.928 --> 16:50.630
OH, YOU KNOW,
GOOD DAYS, BAD DAYS.

16:50.630 --> 16:52.222
GETTIN' THROUGH IT.

16:52.222 --> 16:54.554
IF YOU'RE LOOKING FOR AMANDA,
SHE'S --
 ASLEEP UPSTAIRS?

16:54.554 --> 16:56.896
YEAH. THAT'S GOOD DETECTIVE-ING.

16:56.896 --> 16:58.058
I DON'T KNOW IF YOU HEARD.

16:58.058 --> 16:59.439
WE HAD A LOT OF BURGLAR ALARMS
GO OFF IN TOWN.

16:59.439 --> 17:00.730
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

17:00.730 --> 17:02.692
A SPIKE IN THE POWER GRID.

17:02.692 --> 17:04.814
SO I JUST THOUGHT I'D COME BY
AND CHECK.

17:04.814 --> 17:08.318
CHECK UP
ON HER ANKLE BRACELET?

17:08.318 --> 17:09.858
I CAN ASSURE YOU
IT'S STILL ON.

17:09.858 --> 17:11.451
GOOD.

17:11.451 --> 17:13.492
YEAH, THE MONITORING STATION'S
GONNA REBOOT IT AT 9:00 P.M.

17:13.492 --> 17:15.615
AND WHEN THAT HAPPENS,
HER UNIT WILL RESET

17:15.615 --> 17:17.207
AND SEND OUT AN ALERT.

17:17.207 --> 17:19.368
SO I'LL JUST NEED
TO ADJUST IT.

17:19.368 --> 17:21.751
OH.

17:21.751 --> 17:22.962
FOR REAL?

17:22.962 --> 17:24.334
9:00 P.M., HUH?

17:24.334 --> 17:25.795
AFRAID SO.

17:25.795 --> 17:29.008
[ ALARM BEEPING ]

17:32.762 --> 17:35.635
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

17:35.635 --> 17:36.846
[ BEEPING STOPS ]

17:36.846 --> 17:38.518
SO SHE CLONED THE SIGNAL
FROM HER MONITOR,

17:38.518 --> 17:40.730
LINKED IT TO THIS ONE,
AND TOOK HERS OFF-LINE.

17:40.730 --> 17:42.982
IT'S CLEVER.
 SHE DIDN'T KILL VICTORIA.

17:42.982 --> 17:45.895
YEAH, WELL, I GUESS I'D HOPE MY
FATHER WOULD SAY THE SAME THING.

17:47.026 --> 17:49.068
WELL, WHEREVER SHE IS,

17:49.068 --> 17:50.400
SHE'S BACK ONLINE NOW.

17:53.072 --> 17:56.075
♪♪♪

17:57.076 --> 18:00.079
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

18:15.215 --> 18:16.176
[ CLICK ]

18:16.176 --> 18:17.387
[ DOOR UNLOCKS ]

18:20.810 --> 18:22.021
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

18:54.053 --> 18:58.137
I LIKE THE CANDLESTICKS.
CHAMPAGNE BOTTLES. CLEVER.

18:58.137 --> 19:00.019
MY ROMANTIC HUSBAND.

19:00.019 --> 19:02.182
HE'S INTO REPURPOSING
AND ALL THAT.

19:02.182 --> 19:03.973
MY NEIGHBOR ACROSS THE STREET
WAS THROWING THEM OUT.

19:03.973 --> 19:05.765
I FIGURE ONE MAN'S TRASH...

19:05.765 --> 19:08.107
SPEAKING OF, UM,
DO YOU KNOW WHERE HE IS?

19:08.107 --> 19:10.690
HE WANTED ME TO COME BY, BUT...
 NOT SINCE YESTERDAY.

19:10.690 --> 19:13.823
THE DUDE CLEARED OUT IN A HURRY.
HE AND HIS LADY FRIEND.

19:17.076 --> 19:18.037
HIS LADY FRIEND?

19:20.780 --> 19:23.373
WELL, CAN YOU DESCRIBE HER
FOR ME?

19:23.373 --> 19:25.545
I MEAN, MAYBE HOW OLD SHE WAS?
HER HAIR COLOR?

19:25.545 --> 19:28.047
I DON'T KNOW. IT'S HARD TO SAY.
SHE HAD BIG SUNGLASSES.

19:28.047 --> 19:30.089
AND IT SEEMED LIKE SHE WAS
TRYING TO DRESS DOWN,

19:30.089 --> 19:32.592
BUT THERE WAS SOMETHING...
 [ WHIRRING IN DISTANCE ]

19:32.592 --> 19:34.964
REGAL ABOUT HER.
 Man: GOOD SKIN.

19:34.964 --> 19:37.136
OH, YOU'RE OBSESSED WITH SKIN.
 I'M OBSERVANT.

19:37.136 --> 19:39.219
WHAT ABOUT A NAME?
DID YOU GET A NAME?

19:39.219 --> 19:41.010
[ HELICOPTER WHIRRING OVERHEAD ]

19:41.010 --> 19:44.143
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

19:44.143 --> 19:45.475
[ BRAKES SCREECH ]

19:45.475 --> 19:47.357
Man: [ Amplified voice ] STOP!
PUT YOUR HANDS IN THE AIR.

19:47.357 --> 19:48.858
WE HAVE YOU SURROUNDED.

19:50.189 --> 19:51.070
[ BRAKES SQUEAL ]
 Man: PUT YOUR HANDS UP!

19:51.070 --> 19:53.152
Man: GET ON YOUR KNEES!

19:53.152 --> 19:55.074
Man: GET ON YOUR KNEES NOW!
 ON YOUR KNEES! NOW!

19:55.074 --> 19:56.616
[ OFFICERS
SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY ]

20:00.159 --> 20:02.492
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]
 BEN...

20:02.492 --> 20:05.164
I CAN'T TELL YOU HOW BADLY
I WANTED TO BE WRONG.

20:05.164 --> 20:07.377
PLEASE, YOU GOTTA LISTEN TO ME.

20:07.377 --> 20:09.789
BEN! [ EXHALES ]

20:16.886 --> 20:19.138
OKAY. THANKS.

20:21.761 --> 20:23.973
THE LAWYER SAYS THEY'RE
LOCKING HER UP THROUGH TRIAL.

20:23.973 --> 20:26.346
THEY'RE RESTRICTING VISITORS.
FAMILY ONLY ON A LIMITED BASIS.

20:26.346 --> 20:27.687
CAN THEY DO THAT?

20:27.687 --> 20:29.309
YEAH, THEY DID THAT,
SO YES, THEY CAN.

20:29.309 --> 20:31.851
WHY THE HELL DID YOU LET HER?
 I DIDN'T LET HER DO ANYTHING.

20:31.851 --> 20:33.563
YOU SHOULD'VE MADE HER
STAY PUT

20:33.563 --> 20:35.024
THEN GONE AFTER MASON
YOURSELF.

20:35.024 --> 20:36.526
AND HOW'D THAT WORK OUT
FOR YOU?

20:36.526 --> 20:40.570
COME ON. YOU EVER TALK EMILY
INTO ANYTHING?

20:40.570 --> 20:43.072
WE HAVE TO DO WHAT SHE SHOULD'VE
LET US DO ALL ALONG.

20:43.072 --> 20:45.285
WE HAVE TO PROVE THAT VICTORIA
AND OTHERS FRAMED EMILY.

20:45.285 --> 20:46.536
WHAT OTHERS?

20:46.536 --> 20:47.787
[ SIGHS ]

20:49.669 --> 20:51.250
DEFINITELY MARGAUX, FOR ONE.

20:51.250 --> 20:52.752
WHEN I ASKED HER
IF SHE KNEW ANYTHING,

20:52.752 --> 20:54.834
SHE STORMED OUT OF LUNCH
AND INTO A LeMARCHAL TOWN CAR,

20:54.834 --> 20:56.296
AND THEN I SAW
THE LICENSE PLATE.

20:56.296 --> 20:57.837
LMM 16Q.

20:57.837 --> 21:00.840
NOW THIS IS THE CAR THAT DROPPED
MASON OFF AT THE TRAILER PARK.

21:00.840 --> 21:03.973
LOOK.
 OKAY, SO...

21:03.973 --> 21:06.185
MASON IS BEING SHUTTLED AROUND
IN A LeMARCHAL TOWN CAR.

21:06.185 --> 21:09.148
MARGAUX'S RIGHT IN THE CENTER
OF THIS WHOLE THING.

21:10.690 --> 21:13.313
I'LL TELL AMANDA. THEY'RE
LETTING ME SEE HER THIS MORNING.

21:13.313 --> 21:15.815
TELL HER
WE'RE GETTING HER OUT.

21:15.815 --> 21:19.028
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS,
DOOR OPENS ]

21:27.246 --> 21:30.119
[ DOORKNOB RATTLING ]

21:37.216 --> 21:40.049
[ RATTLING CONTINUES ]

21:40.049 --> 21:41.341
[ BANGING ]

21:41.341 --> 21:43.973
[ RATTLING RESUMES ]

21:43.973 --> 21:45.264
[ GASPS ]

21:45.264 --> 21:48.348
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOIN' HERE?

21:48.348 --> 21:51.351
LOOKING FOR EVIDENCE
TO CLEAR MY INNOCENT FRIEND.

21:51.351 --> 21:53.272
BETTER QUESTION -- WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

21:53.272 --> 21:57.276
OH, I HAVE EVERY RIGHT
AND FULL PERMISSION TO BE HERE.

21:57.276 --> 22:00.360
VICTORIA GRAYSON WAS
MY OWN PERSONAL GUARDIAN ANGEL.

22:00.360 --> 22:01.701
[ SIGHS ] LOUISE-SPEAK.

22:01.701 --> 22:03.903
WELL, LET'S PUT THAT THROUGH
GOOGLE TRANSLATE AND...

22:03.903 --> 22:05.244
YOU'RE HERE TO HELP CLEAN UP

22:05.244 --> 22:06.746
AFTER
YOUR LATE VINDICTIVE FRIEND

22:06.746 --> 22:08.037
AND TIE UP ANY LOOSE ENDS

22:08.037 --> 22:10.119
IN HER CRAZY-ASS ATTEMPT
TO FRAME EMILY.

22:10.119 --> 22:11.120
HMM?
 STOP THAT.

22:11.120 --> 22:13.002
YOU WILL NOT DISRESPECT
HER MEMORY

22:13.002 --> 22:14.003
WHILE STANDING IN HER HOME.

22:14.003 --> 22:15.625
WELL, I CAN'T STAND
IN EMILY'S HOME

22:15.625 --> 22:17.216
BECAUSE YOUR GUARDIAN ANGEL
 BLEW IT UP!

22:17.216 --> 22:19.669
GET OUT! OUT!

22:19.669 --> 22:21.881
YOU KNOW, HOW YOU CAN
LOOK AT THAT WOMAN

22:21.881 --> 22:23.593
AND NOT SEE
WHAT EVERYBODY ELSE SAW,

22:23.593 --> 22:25.425
IT'S... [ SCOFFS ]
IT'S BEYOND ME.

22:25.425 --> 22:27.016
BECAUSE I SAW
WHO SHE REALLY WAS.

22:27.016 --> 22:29.599
NO, YOU SAW
WHO YOU WANTED HER TO BE.

22:31.060 --> 22:34.273
LOUISE, YOU ARE ONE OF THE MOST
LOYAL PEOPLE THAT I KNOW,

22:34.273 --> 22:37.737
AND THAT IS A QUALITY
THAT I TRULY ADORE IN YOU.

22:37.737 --> 22:42.031
BUT IN THIS CASE,
IT WAS AND IS MISPLACED.

22:43.533 --> 22:45.034
YOU'RE WRONG.

22:46.826 --> 22:48.908
VICTORIA MANAGED
THIS WHOLE THING.

22:48.908 --> 22:51.080
AND I KNOW YOU THINK
THE SUN ROSE AND SET WITH HER,

22:51.080 --> 22:53.663
BUT MAYBE THAT'S WHAT SHE
COUNTED ON TO PULL THIS OFF --

22:53.663 --> 22:56.836
YOUR BLIND FAITH.

22:56.836 --> 23:00.049
I AM NOT BLIND.

23:00.049 --> 23:02.632
VICTORIA GRAYSON WAS
THE ONLY PERSON IN THIS WORLD

23:02.632 --> 23:04.213
WHO LOOKED OUT FOR ME.

23:04.213 --> 23:06.135
[ SIGHS ]

23:06.135 --> 23:08.057
YOU KNOW THAT'S NOT TRUE.

23:08.057 --> 23:09.969
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

23:09.969 --> 23:11.220
NO! GO!
 [ SLAPS ARM ]

23:11.220 --> 23:14.684
GET OUT BEFORE I CALL
HOTEL SECURITY!

23:16.225 --> 23:18.518
[ DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES ]

23:18.518 --> 23:20.980
[ Whispers ] SHE'S ALIVE.
 [ DOOR CLOSES ]

23:20.980 --> 23:23.072
[ Lowered voice ]
I AM TELLING YOU,

23:23.072 --> 23:25.905
VICTORIA IS ALIVE.

23:25.905 --> 23:27.116
YOU DON'T KNOW THAT.
SOUNDS CRAZY.

23:27.116 --> 23:29.078
YOU CAN'T KEEP SAYING THAT
PRESUMED DEAD PEOPLE ARE ALIVE.

23:29.078 --> 23:32.411
THINK ABOUT IT. IT MAKES SENSE.
IT'S WHAT I WOULD DO.

23:34.834 --> 23:37.166
ARE YOU OKAY? YOU LOOK PALE.

23:37.166 --> 23:38.297
YEAH. IT'S THE MEDS.

23:38.297 --> 23:40.500
I'M NOT GONNA SIGN UP
FOR ANY MARATHONS, BUT I'M FINE.

23:40.500 --> 23:42.381
LOOK, I'M NOT SAYING
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE,

23:42.381 --> 23:43.753
BUT...
 IT WAS HER.

23:43.753 --> 23:45.174
HOW YOU GONNA PROVE THAT?

23:45.174 --> 23:46.305
THE POLICE HAVE
THE PHYSICAL REMAINS

23:46.305 --> 23:48.137
IDENTIFIED AS
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

23:48.137 --> 23:49.308
YOU HAVE
THE FUZZY RECOLLECTIONS

23:49.308 --> 23:50.760
OF YOUR PALS
IN THE TRAILER PARK.

23:50.760 --> 23:52.101
IT WON'T EVEN MAKE IT
INTO COURT.

23:52.101 --> 23:53.933
THEN WE HAVE TO FIND HER.

23:53.933 --> 23:56.015
OR MASON. BUT I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE TO LOOK.

23:58.147 --> 24:00.610
YOU CAN START
WITH MARGAUX'S CAR SERVICE.

24:00.610 --> 24:03.773
IT WAS A LeMARCHAL TOWN CAR THAT
TOOK MASON TO THE TRAILER PARK.

24:03.773 --> 24:06.365
THEN I NEED MARGAUX.

24:06.365 --> 24:08.618
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN,
YOU -- YOU NEED --

24:08.618 --> 24:12.572
I NEED FIVE MINUTES IN A ROOM
WITH MARGAUX LeMARCHAL.

24:12.572 --> 24:16.245
AMANDA, YOU'RE IN JAIL. HOW...

24:16.245 --> 24:17.627
DAD?

24:17.627 --> 24:19.418
[ THUD ]
 DAD!

24:19.418 --> 24:21.040
[ GROANS ]

24:21.040 --> 24:23.713
DAD! SOMEBODY HELP HIM!

24:23.713 --> 24:26.045
[ BUZZER SOUNDS ]
 HELP! WE NEED HELP IN HERE!

24:26.045 --> 24:28.007
SIR, WE'RE GONNA GET YOU HELP
RIGHT NOW.
 HELP HIM! DO SOMETHING!

24:28.007 --> 24:30.299
DAD!
 Man: WE HAVE
A MEDICAL EMERGENCY.

24:34.393 --> 24:36.145
Nolan: HE'S RESTING AT HOME.

24:36.145 --> 24:39.148
BY THE TIME I GOT TO THE E.R.,
HE WAS AWAKE. HE WAS STABLE.

24:39.148 --> 24:40.770
IT WAS LIKE NOTHING HAPPENED.

24:40.770 --> 24:43.863
THEY'RE RUNNING MORE TESTS,
AND NO RESULTS YET.

24:43.863 --> 24:46.275
SO THEY SENT DAVID HOME.

24:46.275 --> 24:49.368
HE'S DOING OKAY, RIGHT?

24:49.368 --> 24:52.071
[ SCOFFS ]
HE'S GOT LYMPHOMA, JACK.

24:52.071 --> 24:53.282
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

24:53.282 --> 24:54.704
YEAH, I DO.
I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

24:54.704 --> 24:57.496
HE'S GOT THE BEST DOCTORS,
CUTTING-EDGE TREATMENT.

24:57.496 --> 24:59.999
YOU KNOW, IT'S JUST THE IDEA
OF LOSING HIM, AGAIN.

24:59.999 --> 25:01.250
LOOK, I GET IT.

25:01.250 --> 25:03.122
AND I DON'T WANNA TELL YOU
NOT TO WORRY, BUT RIGHT NOW...

25:03.122 --> 25:04.423
NO, NO. YOU'RE RIGHT.
YOU'RE RIGHT, JACK.

25:04.423 --> 25:06.546
I PROMISED DAVID THAT WE'D DO
WHAT EMILY ASKED.

25:06.546 --> 25:08.427
SO... [ INHALES DEEPLY ]

25:08.427 --> 25:10.590
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ] LET'S FOCUS
ON ONE CLARKE AT A TIME.

25:12.592 --> 25:14.594
[ LAUGHS ] THERE HE IS!

25:14.594 --> 25:16.095
IT'S BEEN A WHILE, MAN.
 YEAH.

25:16.095 --> 25:18.137
NOLAN, DARYL. THIS IS THE GUY
I WAS TELLING YOU ABOUT.

25:18.137 --> 25:20.399
HEY. YEAH,
THE POLICE ACADEMY WASHOUT.

25:20.399 --> 25:23.733
THAT'S NOT HOW I DESCRIBED YOU.
BUT I DIDN'T LAST MUCH LONGER.

25:23.733 --> 25:26.906
WELL, SO, UH, JACK SAYS
YOU'RE WORKING PRIVATE SECURITY?

25:26.906 --> 25:28.948
YEAH, FOR MY BROTHER-IN-LAW'S
COMPANY.

25:28.948 --> 25:30.319
HE GOT ME
ON THE GOLD COAST ROTATION --

25:30.319 --> 25:32.361
BANKS, JEWELERS.
YOU KNOW,

25:32.361 --> 25:34.243
PROTECTING 1 PERCENTERS
FROM THE 2 PERCENTERS.

25:34.243 --> 25:35.655
[ CHUCKLES ]
 [ CHUCKLES ]

25:35.655 --> 25:37.156
WELL, WE APPRECIATE
YOU HELPING US OUT.

25:37.156 --> 25:38.497
ANYTHING FOR THIS GUY.

25:38.497 --> 25:40.209
SAVED MY ASS
OUT ON THAT OBSTACLE COURSE.

25:40.209 --> 25:42.622
[ CHUCKLES ]
 HEY, THE WHOLE TIME
YOU WERE A COP,

25:42.622 --> 25:45.214
DID YOU EVER ONCE HAVE TO
JUMP OVER A 16-FOOT WALL?

25:45.214 --> 25:48.467
LET ME TELL YOU WHAT WE NEED.
 [ LAUGHS ]

25:50.009 --> 25:53.132
YES, THAT SEEMS APPROPRIATE.
THANK YOU.

25:53.132 --> 25:55.134
APOLOGIES, HENRI.
THE GRAND PRIX OF NEWS CYCLES.

25:55.134 --> 25:56.345
SO YOU WERE SAYING?

25:56.345 --> 26:00.229
A WREATH NECKLACE
WITH 122 MARQUISE DIAMONDS.

26:00.229 --> 26:03.022
YOU WERE LOOKING FOR SOMETHING
ELEGANT BUT UNDERSTATED?

26:03.022 --> 26:05.104
FOR THE FUNERAL
OF A DEAR FRIEND.

26:05.104 --> 26:07.236
IT'S PERFECT. I'LL TAKE IT.

26:07.236 --> 26:08.898
I'LL HAVE IT FITTED
AND DELIVERED.

26:08.898 --> 26:10.279
MERCI, HENRI.

26:13.242 --> 26:15.534
[ ALARM BLARING ]
 MA'AM, COULD YOU TAKE
A STEP BACK

26:15.534 --> 26:16.746
AND OPEN YOUR PURSE, PLEASE?

26:16.746 --> 26:18.367
NO. [ SCOFFS ] NO,
THE MACHINE MUST BE BROKEN.

26:18.367 --> 26:19.789
PLEASE OPEN THE DOOR.

26:19.789 --> 26:22.201
AS SOON AS YOU TAKE A STEP BACK
AND OPEN YOUR PURSE.

26:22.201 --> 26:25.124
HENRI, COULD YOU CALL OFF
YOUR STORM TROOPER HERE?

26:25.124 --> 26:27.466
I-I AM SORRY, MS. LeMARCHAL.

26:27.466 --> 26:30.469
THE INSURANCE COMPANY INSISTS.

26:30.469 --> 26:32.471
INCROYABLE. OKAY, YOU WANT
TO LOOK IN MY BAG?

26:32.471 --> 26:33.883
LOOK IN MY BAG,

26:33.883 --> 26:36.215
BUT KNOW THAT I WILL NOT
BE BUYING ANYTHING FROM HERE --

26:36.215 --> 26:38.097
MA'AM?

26:38.097 --> 26:40.179
W-- I'VE NEVER SEEN THESE.
 YOURS?

26:40.179 --> 26:42.061
NO, THEY'RE NOT MINE.
I'VE NEVER SEEN --
 WOULD YOU COME WITH ME

26:42.061 --> 26:43.392
TO THE BACK OF THE STORE,
PLEASE, MA'AM?

26:43.392 --> 26:45.354
NO, NO, I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE
EXCEPT OUT.

26:45.354 --> 26:47.026
PLEASE GIVE ME MY BAG
AND OPEN THE DOOR.

26:47.026 --> 26:49.028
MISS, YOU WANNA DIAL IT DOWN?
 NO, YOU DIAL IT DOWN!

26:49.028 --> 26:51.861
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA HOW MUCH
MONEY I'VE SPENT IN THIS STORE?

26:51.861 --> 26:54.033
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.
GET YOUR HANDS OFF ME!
 [ SMACK ]

26:54.033 --> 26:56.195
[ PATRONS GASP ]
 ALL RIGHT, THAT'S IT.
UP AGAINST THE WALL.

26:56.195 --> 26:59.158
BUT THIS IS RIDICULOUS!
WHAT ARE YOU -- UHH!

26:59.158 --> 27:01.741
HENRI, YOU CAN EXPECT A CALL
FROM MY ATTORNEY.
 [ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

27:01.741 --> 27:03.042
[ MARGAUX SCOFFS ]
 Daryl: CAN YOU HOLD HER?

27:03.042 --> 27:05.044
I'M GONNA GO CALL THIS IN.

27:05.044 --> 27:06.045
SHOW'S OVER, PEOPLE.

27:06.045 --> 27:07.246
ARE YOU REALLY DOING THIS?

27:07.246 --> 27:10.209
MS. LeMARCHAL --
 [ SPEAKS FRENCH ]

27:13.803 --> 27:15.174
ALWAYS GOOD
TO SEE YOU, DARYL.

27:15.174 --> 27:17.556
I WOULD'VE DONE THAT FOR FREE.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

27:17.556 --> 27:18.968
RICH PEOPLE.

27:27.106 --> 27:28.567
I DEMAND ANOTHER PHONE CALL.
 YOU ONLY GET ONE.

27:28.567 --> 27:30.690
NOT THE COUNTY'S FAULT
YOUR LAWYER DIDN'T ANSWER.

27:30.690 --> 27:33.442
THIS IS A MISTAKE. YOU WILL SEE,
IT WILL BE IN EVERY PAPER.

27:33.442 --> 27:36.195
YOU CAN TELL THE JUDGE
ALL ABOUT IT IN THE MORNING.

27:36.195 --> 27:38.948
MORNING?
NO, NO, I NEED TO GET OUT TODAY.

27:38.948 --> 27:39.989
WHAT DO YOU MEAN MORNING?!

27:39.989 --> 27:42.742
[ BUZZER SOUNDS, DOOR UNLOCKS ]
 [ SIGHS ]

27:42.742 --> 27:47.416
IT MEANS YOU WERE FRAMED
AT THE WORST POSSIBLE TIME.

27:47.416 --> 27:48.708
AMANDA.

27:48.708 --> 27:50.920
ARRAIGNMENT COURT CLOSES
AT 4:00.

27:50.920 --> 27:53.632
THAT WAS 10 MINUTES AGO.
SUCKS FOR YOU.

27:53.632 --> 27:56.215
OF COURSE YOU WERE
BEHIND THIS.

27:56.215 --> 27:57.556
WELL, THAT'S A THEORY.

27:57.556 --> 28:00.059
[ INHALES DEEPLY ] WE'VE GOT
ALL NIGHT TO DISCUSS IT,

28:00.059 --> 28:01.851
AMONG OTHER THINGS.

28:01.851 --> 28:03.142
NO, I WON'T BE TALKING TO YOU,

28:03.142 --> 28:04.513
AND THERE'S NOTHING
YOU CAN DO ABOUT IT.

28:04.513 --> 28:08.307
MM. YOU'D THINK.

28:08.307 --> 28:11.520
2 LOCKED DOORS, 12 INCHES
OF CINDER BLOCK BETWEEN US.

28:11.520 --> 28:14.153
AND YET...
 HEY, I NEED TO SPEAK TO SOMEONE!

28:14.153 --> 28:16.405
[ DOOR SLIDES OPEN ]

28:18.197 --> 28:20.699
HOW DID YOU...

28:20.699 --> 28:22.782
[ UNLOCKS DOOR ]

28:22.782 --> 28:26.205
[ KEYS CLATTER ]
 YOU HAVE MORE IMPORTANT THINGS
TO WORRY ABOUT.

28:29.168 --> 28:32.922
HURTING ME WON'T CHANGE THE FACT
THAT YOU MURDERED VICTORIA.

28:32.922 --> 28:35.254
YOU KNOW I DIDN'T.

28:35.254 --> 28:37.506
YOU DON'T HAVE TO GET HURT.

28:37.506 --> 28:40.049
JUST ANSWER MY QUESTIONS.

28:40.049 --> 28:44.013
HOW DID VICTORIA SET ME UP?
WHOSE BODY WAS IN MY HOUSE?

28:44.013 --> 28:45.554
AND EXTRA BONUS POINTS...

28:47.056 --> 28:49.018
WHERE'S VICTORIA?

28:49.018 --> 28:50.519
I KNOW SHE'S ALIVE.

28:50.519 --> 28:51.690
YOU ARE DELUSIONAL.

28:51.690 --> 28:53.232
DELUSIONAL
WITH NOTHING TO LOSE.

28:54.693 --> 28:57.696
THE GUARDS SCHEDULE GIVES US
EXACTLY 11 MINUTES,

28:57.696 --> 29:01.490
WHICH IS...FOUR MINUTES LONGER
THAN I'LL NEED.

29:02.621 --> 29:04.033
[ KEYS JANGLE ]

29:05.034 --> 29:06.455
WHAT IS ALL THIS?

29:06.455 --> 29:09.668
I TRAINED COMPREHENSIVELY
TO GET REVENGE FOR MY FATHER.

29:09.668 --> 29:11.210
DURING MY SCHOOLING,

29:11.210 --> 29:14.043
I LEARNED A LITTLE SOMETHING
CALLED "PRACTICAL MUNITIONS."

29:14.043 --> 29:16.715
THE ART OF TAKING ANYTHING FROM
YOUR IMMEDIATE ENVIRONMENT

29:16.715 --> 29:19.088
AND TURNING IT INTO A WEAPON.
 YOU'RE BLUFFING.

29:21.090 --> 29:24.093
BATTERIES FROM A FLASHLIGHT
A GUARD MISPLACED,

29:24.093 --> 29:26.225
A SET OF STEEL KEYS...
 [ KEYS JANGLE ]

29:26.225 --> 29:28.938
THERE YOU HAVE IT.

29:28.938 --> 29:31.150
ONE WEAPON, NO WAITING.

29:31.150 --> 29:32.561
WHAT IS THE MATTER WITH YOU?

29:32.561 --> 29:34.103
WHAT IS THE MATTER WITH YOU,
 MARGAUX?

29:34.103 --> 29:35.985
YOU FILLED THE EMPTY SPACE
IN YOUR LIFE

29:35.985 --> 29:37.817
WITH A LYING,
DANGEROUS FANATIC,

29:37.817 --> 29:39.158
AND THAT IS WHAT YOU BECAME.

29:39.158 --> 29:42.201
I DON'T HAVE SYMPATHY FOR YOU.
YOU BROUGHT THIS ON YOURSELF.

29:42.201 --> 29:44.533
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING.
 AND I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

29:44.533 --> 29:46.866
[ GRUNTING ]
 NOW YOU LISTEN TO ME.

29:46.866 --> 29:48.037
MY FATHER IS ILL,

29:48.037 --> 29:50.249
AND I REFUSE TO SPEND THE LAST
DAYS OF HIS LIFE IN PRISON

29:50.249 --> 29:51.580
FOR SOMETHING
THAT I DIDN'T DO.

29:51.580 --> 29:53.462
SO LAST QUESTION, MARGAUX,

29:53.462 --> 29:56.215
AND THEN I START
WITH THE CHEEKBONES.

29:56.215 --> 29:58.177
I'M ONLY GONNA ASK YOU ONCE.

29:58.177 --> 29:59.178
[ GASPS ]

29:59.178 --> 30:02.591
HOW DO YOU WANT TO SPEND
THE NEXT SEVEN MINUTES?

30:28.577 --> 30:29.828
[ SNIFFS ]

30:32.711 --> 30:34.413
[ Whispers ]
I HOPE YOU REST IN PEACE.

30:50.469 --> 30:52.932
[ GASPS ] AAH!

30:52.932 --> 30:54.183
UHH! OW!

30:59.148 --> 31:00.649
[ GASPS ]

31:03.903 --> 31:05.114
[ GASPS ]

31:07.746 --> 31:09.118
[ BUZZER SOUNDS ]

31:10.409 --> 31:12.081
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

31:15.955 --> 31:17.917
I HEARD YOU WANTED TO SEE ME.

31:17.917 --> 31:20.169
[ SNIFFLES ]

31:20.169 --> 31:21.710
I DIDN'T KNOW IF YOU'D COME.

31:21.710 --> 31:23.502
WELL, I DON'T HAVE A CHOICE.

31:23.502 --> 31:25.304
YOU SAID YOU HAD NEW INFORMATION
ABOUT THIS MURDER,

31:25.304 --> 31:28.427
SO LET'S HEAR IT.

31:28.427 --> 31:30.219
THERE WAS NO MURDER.

31:30.219 --> 31:32.061
VICTORIA IS ALIVE.
 ALL RIGHT.

31:32.061 --> 31:34.013
LOOK, I DON'T GET TO DECIDE
AS TO WHETHER OR NOT TO SHOW UP,

31:34.013 --> 31:35.224
BUT I DO GET TO DECIDE
WHEN I LEAVE.

31:35.224 --> 31:36.565
BEN, LISTEN TO ME.

31:36.565 --> 31:39.518
SHE STAGED A FAKE MURDER,
SET ME UP, AND TOOK OFF.

31:39.518 --> 31:41.650
WE IDENTIFIED HER BODY,
EMILY.

31:41.650 --> 31:43.022
WE HAVE DENTAL RECORDS
AND X-RAYS.

31:43.022 --> 31:44.863
THEY'RE NOT HERS.
 [ SIGHS ]

31:44.863 --> 31:48.077
SHE SWITCHED THEM WITH A WOMAN
NAMED MARY GAINES.

31:48.077 --> 31:49.158
SHE DIED LAST WEEK.

31:49.158 --> 31:50.869
DID SHE NOW? MARY GAINES?

31:50.869 --> 31:52.581
SO THIS NEW INFORMATION

31:52.581 --> 31:54.083
JUST CAME TO YOU LAST NIGHT
IN A DREAM?

31:54.083 --> 31:55.294
OR BY CARRIER PIGEON?

31:55.294 --> 31:59.168
PLEASE, JUST STOP ALREADY.

31:59.168 --> 32:02.171
YOU KNOW,
I SAW YOUR FATHER EARLIER.

32:02.171 --> 32:04.803
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
THE DAMAGE THAT YOU'RE CAUSING?

32:04.803 --> 32:06.005
OR THE PEOPLE THAT
YOU'RE HURTING OUT THERE?

32:06.005 --> 32:09.178
YES, BEN, AND I KNOW THAT
YOU'RE ONE OF THOSE PEOPLE.

32:09.178 --> 32:12.051
LOOK, I AM SORRY FOR THE WAY
THAT I TREATED YOU,

32:12.051 --> 32:14.393
FOR THINKING THAT
I DIDN'T HAVE TO BE HONEST

32:14.393 --> 32:17.146
BECAUSE SOMEHOW MY LIFE
WAS DIFFERENT.

32:17.146 --> 32:18.687
[ SIGHS ]

32:18.687 --> 32:20.980
I KNOW I HAVEN'T BEEN THE KIND
OF PERSON THAT YOU CAN TRUST,

32:20.980 --> 32:22.611
BUT PLEASE...

32:22.611 --> 32:26.365
YOU CAN TRUST ME NOW.

32:26.365 --> 32:28.907
I KNOW HOW
VICTORIA PULLED THIS OFF.

32:32.161 --> 32:33.332
TELL ME.

32:37.206 --> 32:38.497
I THINK
THE SEED WAS PLANTED

32:38.497 --> 32:40.379
THE NIGHT I GAVE
THAT INTERVIEW...

32:40.379 --> 32:44.133
VICTORIA, IF YOU'RE WATCHING,

32:44.133 --> 32:46.885
IT IS IN YOUR HANDS
TO END THIS.

32:46.885 --> 32:50.759
...AND THE WHOLE WORLD
TURNED AGAINST HER.

32:50.759 --> 32:54.683
SHE READ UP ON HOW TO FAKE
ONE'S OWN DEATH

32:54.683 --> 32:56.975
AND GET AWAY...

32:56.975 --> 32:58.147
I WOULD BE REMISS

32:58.147 --> 33:00.769
IF I DIDN'T THANK YOU
FOR THAT BRILLIANT IDEA

33:00.769 --> 33:02.651
I FOUND ON THAT FLASH DRIVE
OF YOURS.

33:02.651 --> 33:04.903
SHE KNEW
THAT WITHOUT A BODY,

33:04.903 --> 33:08.237
REMAINS THAT COULD BE IDENTIFIED
AS HER OWN, IT WOULDN'T WORK.

33:08.237 --> 33:11.410
SOMETIMES DESPERATION
BREEDS RESULTS.

33:11.410 --> 33:15.614
AND IN THIS CASE, THE RESULT WAS
AN UNCLAIMED BODY IN NEW JERSEY.

33:15.614 --> 33:16.995
SOMEONE WHO WOULDN'T
BE MISSED.

33:16.995 --> 33:22.831
AND WITH THAT, VICTORIA SET
HER PLAN IN MOTION.

33:22.831 --> 33:24.173
UHH! UHH!

33:27.046 --> 33:28.047
Emily: SHE MADE IT LOOK LIKE

33:28.047 --> 33:30.429
I ATTACKED HER
IN A PARKING GARAGE,

33:30.429 --> 33:31.840
MADE SURE
THERE WERE WITNESSES

33:31.840 --> 33:34.893
WHO WOULD SAY AS MUCH
TO THE POLICE.

33:34.893 --> 33:36.515
[ CRACK ]

33:36.515 --> 33:40.099
SHE STAGED HER PENTHOUSE TO LOOK
LIKE SHE WAS ASSAULTED...

33:40.099 --> 33:41.270
[ SHATTERS ]

33:41.270 --> 33:46.195
SEASONED LIBERALLY
WITH HER BLOOD...

33:51.110 --> 33:56.205
THE REST OF WHICH SHE GAVE
TO MASON TO PLANT IN MY CAR.

33:58.457 --> 34:00.209
SHE ALTERED HER HANDWRITING
JUST ENOUGH

34:00.209 --> 34:02.000
TO MAKE
HER SUICIDE NOTE LOOK

34:02.000 --> 34:05.464
LIKE A GOOD
BUT NOT GREAT FORGERY.

34:08.087 --> 34:10.549
ALL THAT WAS LEFT
WAS THE BIG FINISH...

34:17.096 --> 34:18.387
MAKING THE WORLD BELIEVE

34:18.387 --> 34:21.100
THAT I WAS A BIGGER MONSTER
THAN SHE HAD EVER BEEN.

34:24.943 --> 34:26.145
[ CRACKLING ]

34:26.145 --> 34:28.987
A MONSTER WHO BURNED
THE QUEEN ALIVE

34:28.987 --> 34:31.029
IN THE CASTLE
SHE USED TO OWN.

34:37.116 --> 34:40.458
[ EXPLOSION ]

34:42.911 --> 34:44.703
WOW. THAT'S...

34:46.004 --> 34:49.338
SO...WHERE IS SHE NOW?

34:51.380 --> 34:52.630
I DON'T KNOW.

34:55.013 --> 34:56.554
I SEE.

34:56.554 --> 34:57.846
SO SHE STAGED
THIS WHOLE THING.

34:57.846 --> 35:01.350
SHE FOOLED EVERYONE ON EARTH
 BUT YOU

35:01.350 --> 35:02.811
AND JUST DISAPPEARED.

35:04.313 --> 35:06.024
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME. YOU DON'T
THINK I'M TELLING THE TRUTH.

35:06.024 --> 35:09.067
NO, IT -- IT'S NOT THAT I DON'T
THINK YOU'RE TELLING THE TRUTH.

35:09.067 --> 35:12.691
IT'S THAT I DON'T THINK
YOU KNOW HOW TO TELL THE TRUTH.

35:12.691 --> 35:14.863
ALL RIGHT, I DON'T THINK THERE'S
ANY DIFFERENCE IN YOUR HEAD

35:14.863 --> 35:17.996
BETWEEN THE STORIES THAT
YOU SPIN AND ACTUAL FACTS.

35:17.996 --> 35:20.038
AND THAT IS
WHAT MAKES YOU DANGEROUS.

35:20.038 --> 35:22.661
BEN, PLEASE, LISTEN TO ME.
SHE IS OUT THERE.

35:22.661 --> 35:26.124
THIS ONE TIME, I NEED YOU
TO BELIEVE ME.

35:26.124 --> 35:28.006
I KNOW YOU DO.

35:29.708 --> 35:32.251
BUT... [ SIGHS ]

35:32.251 --> 35:33.302
I DON'T.

35:33.302 --> 35:35.714
[ HANGS UP RECEIVER ]

35:38.517 --> 35:40.018
[ HANGS UP RECEIVER ]

35:40.018 --> 35:42.391
[ DOOR OPENS, BUZZER SOUNDS ]

35:42.391 --> 35:43.812
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

35:48.106 --> 35:49.438
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS,
TELEPHONE RINGING ]

35:49.438 --> 35:51.730
EXCUSE ME? DETECTIVE?

35:51.730 --> 35:53.942
MS. ELLIS.
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

35:53.942 --> 35:55.904
WELL, YES. I ASKED FOR YOU,
AND THEY SENT ME HERE.

35:55.904 --> 35:56.985
IS THIS OKAY?

35:56.985 --> 35:59.117
YES, PLEASE, SIT DOWN.

35:59.117 --> 36:00.539
HOW CAN I HELP YOU?

36:00.539 --> 36:02.991
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

36:02.991 --> 36:06.164
SO I FOUND SOMETHING, AND...

36:06.164 --> 36:07.546
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

36:07.546 --> 36:10.249
SO, UM...

36:13.091 --> 36:14.463
THIS WAS
IN VICTORIA GRAYSON'S CLOSET.

36:14.463 --> 36:18.467
I FOUND IT HIDDEN
INSIDE A GARMENT BAG.

36:25.013 --> 36:26.685
YOU FOUND THIS
IN VICTORIA'S PENTHOUSE?

36:26.685 --> 36:28.647
DO YOU RECOGNIZE IT?

36:28.647 --> 36:30.979
[ BAG RUSTLES ]

36:30.979 --> 36:32.401
LOOKS LIKE THE ONE

36:32.401 --> 36:35.524
VICTORIA SAID EMILY WAS WEARING
WHEN SHE WAS ATTACKED.

36:35.524 --> 36:37.115
LOOK...

36:37.115 --> 36:40.158
I CAN'T BELIEVE I'M SAYING THIS,
BUT, UM...

36:40.158 --> 36:43.081
WHAT IF
VICTORIA KILLED HERSELF

36:43.081 --> 36:46.084
AND MADE IT LOOK
LIKE EMILY DID IT?

36:51.250 --> 36:54.293
YOU'RE A LONG WAY
FROM THE HAMPTONS, DETECTIVE.

36:54.293 --> 36:56.715
YEAH.
 SIGN HERE.

36:56.715 --> 36:59.047
AND I'LL NEED THE NAME
OF THE DECEASED.

36:59.047 --> 37:01.179
MARY GAINES.

37:01.179 --> 37:02.220
OKAY. YEAH.

37:02.220 --> 37:06.224
UH, DIED LAST WEEK,
STILL UNCLAIMED. DRAWER A12.

37:09.348 --> 37:12.271
HUH. UH...

37:12.271 --> 37:14.192
THERE MUST BE A MISTAKE.

37:14.192 --> 37:15.854
BODIES DON'T JUST DISAPPEAR.

37:15.854 --> 37:20.198
NO. NOT USUALLY.

37:20.198 --> 37:22.741
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

37:22.741 --> 37:24.993
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOUR GUY HAS JUICE.

37:24.993 --> 37:27.035
GETTIN' A JUDGE ON THE PHONE
AT HOME?

37:27.035 --> 37:28.036
AM I DONE HERE?

37:28.036 --> 37:29.828
FREE TO GO.

37:29.828 --> 37:31.370
ARRAIGNMENT'S TOMORROW.

37:34.082 --> 37:35.754
MARGAUX.

37:35.754 --> 37:36.965
LOUISE?

37:36.965 --> 37:38.427
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

37:38.427 --> 37:40.048
YOUR OFFICE SAID YOU WERE
GETTIN' OUT TODAY.

37:40.048 --> 37:42.140
AND WE NEED TO TALK.
 I'M IN A HURRY.

37:42.140 --> 37:44.433
LISTEN, I SPOKE
WITH DETECTIVE HUNTER,

37:44.433 --> 37:46.224
AND --
 WAIT. WHY?

37:47.976 --> 37:50.018
[ Whispers ] I THINK
VICTORIA LIED TO US.

37:50.018 --> 37:51.730
WHEN I WAS PACKING UP
HER PENTHOUSE,

37:51.730 --> 37:54.022
I FOUND THE HOODIE
THAT SHE SAID EMILY WAS WEARING

37:54.022 --> 37:55.734
WHEN SHE SUPPOSEDLY
ATTACKED HER.

37:55.734 --> 37:58.657
NO, EMILY DID ATTACK HER.
 IF SHE LIED ABOUT THAT,

37:58.657 --> 38:00.859
SHE COULD'VE LIED
ABOUT A LOT OF THINGS.

38:00.859 --> 38:03.111
AND YOU TOLD DETECTIVE HUNTER
THIS?

38:03.111 --> 38:04.363
I THINK NOLAN WAS RIGHT.

38:04.363 --> 38:05.784
WHEN I TALKED TO HIM
AT THE PENTHOUSE --

38:05.784 --> 38:08.076
WHOA, WHOA, WAIT. NOLAN?

38:08.076 --> 38:09.748
NOLAN ROSS WAS
IN VICTORIA'S PENTHOUSE?

38:09.748 --> 38:12.170
WELL, HE WAS TRYING TO SNEAK IN
THROUGH THE FIRE DOOR.

38:12.170 --> 38:16.124
BUT HE WAS LOOKING FOR PROOF
THAT VICTORIA HAD FRAMED EMILY.

38:16.124 --> 38:18.337
NOLAN IS A LIAR
AND MANIPULATOR.

38:18.337 --> 38:20.629
YOU KNOW THAT BETTER THAN
ANYONE.

38:20.629 --> 38:23.422
HOW MANY TIMES ARE YOU GOING
TO LET HIM DO THIS TO YOU?

38:23.422 --> 38:26.425
BUT HE WASN'T LYING THIS TIME.
I'M CERTAIN OF IT.

38:26.425 --> 38:27.726
YOU MEAN WHEN YOU CAUGHT HIM

38:27.726 --> 38:29.768
BREAKING INTO
VICTORIA'S HOTEL ROOM?

38:29.768 --> 38:33.352
SOMETHING WE CAN ASSUME
HE'S DONE BEFORE.

38:33.352 --> 38:35.103
ARE YOU SAYING
HE PLANTED THE HOODIE?

38:35.103 --> 38:37.736
[ SIGHS ] OF COURSE HE DID.
THAT'S WHAT HE DOES.

38:37.736 --> 38:39.738
HE WANTED YOU TO FIND IT.

38:41.860 --> 38:44.363
WELL, IF THAT'S THE CASE, THEN
I PLAYED RIGHT INTO HIS HANDS.

38:45.994 --> 38:48.116
[ Whispers ] MARGAUX,
I DON'T FEEL SO GOOD.

38:48.116 --> 38:49.658
[ SNIFFLES ]

38:49.658 --> 38:51.119
MA CHèRE, YOU'RE EXHAUSTED.
AND WHO CAN BLAME YOU?

38:51.119 --> 38:53.121
IT'S BEEN A TERRIBLE WEEK
FOR ALL OF US.

38:56.004 --> 38:57.626
GO PUT SOME COLD WATER
ON YOUR FACE.

38:57.626 --> 38:59.628
THEN I'LL TAKE YOU HOME.

38:59.628 --> 39:01.049
[ SNIFFLES ]

39:05.924 --> 39:07.766
IT'S MADEMOISELLE LeMARCHAL.

39:07.766 --> 39:10.058
I NEED TO RETAIN YOUR SERVICES
IMMEDIATELY.

39:10.058 --> 39:11.640
IT'S URGENT.

39:15.734 --> 39:18.186
NO. NO, THAT CAN'T BE.
THEY SAID THEY CAUGHT IT EARLY.

39:18.186 --> 39:20.859
WELL, THAT WAS BASED ON
THE INITIAL TESTS.

39:20.859 --> 39:24.152
THEN AFTER THE SEIZURE,
THEY RAN DIFFERENT TESTS.

39:24.152 --> 39:25.484
IT SPREAD.

39:25.484 --> 39:29.157
IT'S IN MY BRAIN.

39:29.157 --> 39:30.789
WELL, SO THEY'LL
TREAT THAT, TOO,

39:30.789 --> 39:32.080
WITH MORE CHEMOTHERAPY,
RIGHT?

39:32.080 --> 39:33.792
NO.

39:33.792 --> 39:35.624
NO, THEY STOPPED
THE CHEMOTHERAPY.

39:38.046 --> 39:39.758
AND REPLACING IT WITH WHAT?
 NOTHING.

39:39.758 --> 39:41.630
STAGE IV LYMPHOMA.

39:41.630 --> 39:42.961
THERE'S NO MORE WAYS
TO FIGHT IT.

39:42.961 --> 39:45.213
WELL, THAT'S BECAUSE THEY AREN'T
TRYING HARD ENOUGH.

39:45.213 --> 39:47.846
HOW LONG?
HOW -- HOW MANY YEARS?

39:47.846 --> 39:49.057
NOT YEARS.

39:49.057 --> 39:50.809
MONTHS.

39:50.809 --> 39:54.352
THEY SAID MAYBE SIX MONTHS
IF I'M LUCKY.

39:54.352 --> 39:57.105
NO, I DON'T BELIEVE THAT.
NEITHER DO YOU.

39:57.105 --> 39:58.977
AMANDA --
 [ Voice breaks ] DOCTORS ARE
WRONG ALL THE TIME.

39:58.977 --> 40:00.779
THIS IS ONE OF THOSE TIMES.

40:00.779 --> 40:03.442
WE WILL SEE SPECIALISTS.
WE WILL GET OTHER OPINIONS.

40:03.442 --> 40:05.193
I DID.
I GOT THE SAME OPINIONS.

40:05.193 --> 40:06.404
I CAN GET MORE,
BUT IT WON'T CHANGE.

40:06.404 --> 40:09.027
YOU DON'T KNOW THAT.
YOU DON'T KNOW ANYTHING.

40:09.027 --> 40:11.199
THERE ARE CLINICAL TRIALS,
EXPERIMENTAL DRUGS.

40:11.199 --> 40:13.291
I HAVE MONEY TO SPEND
ON THIS.

40:13.291 --> 40:15.033
NOLAN HAS MONEY
TO SPEND ON THIS.

40:15.033 --> 40:16.455
IF WE HAVE TO FUND
OUR OWN DAMN LAB,

40:16.455 --> 40:18.336
THAT IS WHAT WE WILL DO.

40:20.038 --> 40:22.000
HOW DID YOU LEARN
TO FIGHT SO HARD?

40:22.000 --> 40:24.753
SAY IT, DAD.

40:24.753 --> 40:26.965
[ Voice breaks ]
TELL ME THAT IS WHAT WE WILL DO.

40:29.598 --> 40:30.969
THAT'S WHAT WE'LL DO.

40:34.182 --> 40:35.143
YEAH.

41:05.133 --> 41:06.505
[ CATALOGUE THUDS ]

41:15.013 --> 41:18.186
[ UNLOCKS ]

41:18.186 --> 41:19.978
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

41:41.079 --> 41:43.121
[ FAUCET SQUEAKS ]

41:43.121 --> 41:46.124
[ WATER RUNNING ]

41:56.054 --> 41:57.936
SON OF A BITCH.

41:59.688 --> 42:01.399
YOU ARE ALIVE.

42:03.231 --> 42:05.103
[ BLADE WHOOSHES ]
 [ GASPS ]

42:05.103 --> 42:06.695
[ GASPING ]

42:06.695 --> 42:09.277
[ BREATHING UNEVENLY ]

42:09.277 --> 42:11.780
NEVER GO TO NEW JERSEY
ON BUSINESS.

42:11.780 --> 42:13.652
[ GASPS ]

42:13.652 --> 42:15.574
[ THUD ]
 [ GASPS ] YOU --

42:15.574 --> 42:17.866
SHH.

42:17.866 --> 42:20.579
[ BREATHES UNEVENLY ]
